                                color: #000;
                            ">${isPassed ? 'Congratulations!' : 'Better Luck Next Time'}</h3>

                            <div class="name-certi" style="
                                display: block;
                                margin: 0 50px 20px;
                                border-bottom: 2px solid #000;
                            ">
                                <h1 style="
                                    font-size: 70px;
                                    letter-spacing: 2px;
                                    text-transform: capitalize;
                                    font-family: 'Luxurious Script', cursive;
                                    margin: 0 0 5px 0;
                                    color: #000;
